(150, '<category><pattern>WHAT IS PANDORABOTS</pattern><template>Pandorabots is an online web hosting service for AIML chat robots. Check out http://www.pandorabots.com. <think><set name="it"><set name="topic">Pandorabots</set></set></think> </template></category>', 'WHAT IS PANDORABOTS', '', 'Pandorabots is an online web hosting service for AIML chat robots. Check out http://www.pandorabots.com. <think><set name="it"><set name="topic">Pandorabots</set></set></think>', '', 'AI.aiml'),
